                                        <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidEchoOtherText, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="100" Margin="4,0,0,0" Visibility="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidEchoOther, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}"/>
                                    </StackPanel>
                                </WrapPanel>

                                <Grid Margin="0,0,0,12">
                                    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                                    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                    <TextBlock Text="边界：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                                    <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1">
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystBound" Content="规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidBoundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=规则}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystBound" Content="不规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidBoundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=不规则}"/>
                                    </WrapPanel>
                                    <TextBlock Text="声影：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="2"/>
                                    <WrapPanel Grid.Column="3">
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystShadow" Content="有" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidShadow, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=有}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystShadow" Content="无" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidShadow, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=无}"/>
                                    </WrapPanel>
                                </Grid>

                                <TextBlock Text="血流：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <StackPanel>
                                    <WrapPanel>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidFlow" Content="无血流" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidHasNoFlow}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidFlow" Content="有血流" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidHasFlow}"/>
                                    </WrapPanel>
                                    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="20,8,0,0" Visibility="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidHasFlow, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}">
                                        <TextBlock Text="程度：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidFlowAmt" Content="少量" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidFlowAmount, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=少量}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidFlowAmt" Content="中量" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidFlowAmount, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=中量}"/>
                                        <RadioButton GroupName="SolidFlowAmt" Content="丰富" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.SolidFlowAmount, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=丰富}"/>
                                    </StackPanel>
                                </StackPanel>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Border>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="病灶的边界：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystLesionBound" Content="规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.Boundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=规则}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystLesionBound" Content="不规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.Boundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=不规则}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,0">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="肿物整体血流评分：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystFlowScore" Content="1" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=1}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystFlowScore" Content="2" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=2}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystFlowScore" Content="3" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=3}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidCystFlowScore" Content="4" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidCyst.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=4}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Expander>

                <!-- D. 实性肿物 -->
                <Expander Style="{StaticResource CollapsibleCard}" Visibility="{Binding Report.HasSolidMass, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}">
                    <Expander.Header>
                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                            <Border Width="4" Height="24" Background="White" CornerRadius="2" VerticalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,0,12,0"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="D. 实性肿物" Foreground="White" FontSize="18" FontWeight="Bold" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                        </StackPanel>
                    </Expander.Header>
                    <StackPanel>
                        
                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="大小：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Grid.Column="1">
                                <TextBox helpers:TextBoxHelpers.IsNumeric="True" Text="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Length, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="48"/>
                                <TextBlock Text="×" Margin="4,0"/>
                                <TextBox helpers:TextBoxHelpers.IsNumeric="True" Text="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Width, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="48"/>
                                <TextBlock Text="×" Margin="4,0"/>
                                <TextBox helpers:TextBoxHelpers.IsNumeric="True" Text="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Height, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="48"/>
                                <TextBlock Text="cm" Style="{StaticResource Text.Unit}"/>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="位置：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassLoc" Content="左附件" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=左附件}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassLoc" Content="右附件" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=右附件}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassLoc" Content="子宫后方" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=子宫后方}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassLoc" Content="子宫前方" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=子宫前方}"/>
                                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                                    <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassLoc" Content="其他" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=其他}"/>
                                    <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.SolidMass.LocationOther, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="100" Margin="8,0,0,0" Visibility="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Location, Converter={StaticResource RadioToVis}, ConverterParameter=其他}"/>
                                </StackPanel>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="声影：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassShadow" Content="有" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Shadow, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=有}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassShadow" Content="无" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Shadow, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=无}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="病灶的回声：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassEchoUni" Content="均匀" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.EchoUniformity, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=均匀}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassEchoUni" Content="不均匀" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.EchoUniformity, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=不均匀}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="病灶的边界：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassBound" Content="规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Boundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=规则}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassBound" Content="不规则" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.Boundary, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=不规则}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="病灶回声类型：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassEcho" Content="低回声" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.EchoType, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=低回声}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassEcho" Content="等回声" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.EchoType, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=等回声}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassEcho" Content="高回声" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.EchoType, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=高回声}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,0">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="血流评分：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassFlowScore" Content="1" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=1}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassFlowScore" Content="2" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=2}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassFlowScore" Content="3" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=3}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="SolidMassFlowScore" Content="4" IsChecked="{Binding Report.SolidMass.BloodFlowScore, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=4}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Expander>

                <!-- 合并积液 -->
                <Expander Style="{StaticResource CollapsibleCard}">
                    <Expander.Header>
                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                            <Border Width="4" Height="24" Background="White" CornerRadius="2" VerticalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,0,12,0"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="合并积液" Foreground="White" FontSize="18" FontWeight="Bold" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                        </StackPanel>
                    </Expander.Header>
                    <StackPanel>

                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <RadioButton GroupName="Fluid" Content="无" IsChecked="{Binding Report.HasNoFluid}"/>
                            <RadioButton GroupName="Fluid" Content="有" IsChecked="{Binding Report.HasFluid}"/>
                        </StackPanel>

                        <StackPanel Visibility="{Binding Report.HasFluid, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}">
                            <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding Report.FluidLocations}">
                                <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                        <WrapPanel/>
                                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                    <DataTemplate>
                                        <Border Background="White" BorderBrush="{StaticResource Brush.BorderLight}" BorderThickness="1.5" CornerRadius="8" Padding="14,10" Margin="0,0,12,12">
                                            <StackPanel>
                                                <CheckBox IsChecked="{Binding IsSelected}" Content="{Binding Name}" Margin="0,0,0,8" FontWeight="Medium"/>
                                                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Visibility="{Binding IsSelected, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}">
                                                    <TextBlock Text="深度：" Style="{StaticResource Text.LabelSecondary}"/>
                                                    <TextBox helpers:TextBoxHelpers.IsNumeric="True" Text="{Binding Depth, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="60" Height="32"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="cm" Style="{StaticResource Text.Unit}" Margin="4,0,0,0"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </Border>
                                    </DataTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl>
                            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="0,8,0,0">
                                <CheckBox Content="其他" IsChecked="{Binding Report.HasFluidOther}" Margin="0,0,8,0"/>
                                <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.FluidOtherLocation, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="200" Visibility="{Binding Report.HasFluidOther, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}"/>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </StackPanel>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Expander>

                <!-- 结论与备注区 -->
                <Expander Style="{StaticResource CollapsibleCard}">
                    <Expander.Header>
                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                            <Border Width="4" Height="24" Background="White" CornerRadius="2" VerticalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,0,12,0"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="结论与备注区" Foreground="White" FontSize="18" FontWeight="Bold" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                        </StackPanel>
                    </Expander.Header>
                    <StackPanel>

                        <!-- 超声提示 -->
                        <Border Background="#F0F7FF" CornerRadius="8" Padding="16,12" Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <TextBlock Text="超声提示" FontWeight="SemiBold" FontSize="16" Foreground="{StaticResource Brush.Primary}"/>
                        </Border>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="子宫（描述）：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.UterusDescription, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Grid.Column="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" Height="60" VerticalContentAlignment="Top" Padding="8"/>
                        </Grid>

                        <TextBlock Text="子宫内膜（多选）：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                        <WrapPanel Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <CheckBox Content="子宫内膜增生" IsChecked="{Binding Report.IsEndoHyperplasia}"/>
                            <CheckBox Content="子宫内膜息肉" IsChecked="{Binding Report.IsEndoPolyp}"/>
                            <CheckBox Content="子宫内膜癌" IsChecked="{Binding Report.IsEndoCancer}"/>
                            <CheckBox Content="子宫黏膜下肌瘤" IsChecked="{Binding Report.IsSubmucosalMyoma}"/>
                            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                                <CheckBox Content="其他" IsChecked="{Binding Report.IsEndoOther}"/>
                                <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.EndoOtherText, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Width="150" Margin="8,0,0,0" Visibility="{Binding Report.IsEndoOther, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}"/>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </WrapPanel>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="O-RADS 分级：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <WrapPanel Grid.Column="1" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 0" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 0}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 1" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 1}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 2" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 2}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 3" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 3}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 4" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 4}"/>
                                <RadioButton GroupName="ORads" Content="O-RADS 5" IsChecked="{Binding Report.ORadsLevel, Converter={StaticResource RadioBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=O-RADS 5}"/>
                            </WrapPanel>
                        </Grid>

                        <!-- 注明 -->
                        <Border Background="#F0F7FF" CornerRadius="8" Padding="16,12" Margin="0,20,0,20">
                            <TextBlock Text="注明" FontWeight="SemiBold" FontSize="16" Foreground="{StaticResource Brush.Primary}"/>
                        </Border>
                        <Border Background="#F8F9FA" BorderBrush="{StaticResource Brush.BorderLight}" BorderThickness="1.5" CornerRadius="10" Padding="20" Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,8">
                                    <Run Text="如果存在一个以上的附件肿物，只评估具有最复杂超声形态的肿物，当所有肿物的超声形态是相似的，评估最大的一个或超声最容易探及的一个。" FontSize="12"/>
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,8">
                                    <Run Text="实性成分突出囊壁大于 3mm，则称为乳头。如果不确定是否存在实性的乳头状突起，则按照存在来记录。畸胎瘤中的高回声团、子宫内膜异位囊肿内壁的血液凝固不能视为乳头状突起。" FontSize="12"/>
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,8">
                                    <Run Text="血流评分：主观评价肿物整体的彩色多普勒血流分布情况，包括囊壁，分隔，实性成分。0 分：无血流；1 分：少量血流；2 分：中等量血流；3 分：丰富血流。" FontSize="12"/>
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
                                    <Run Text="至少存在一个完整的分隔的囊肿为多房囊肿，如果囊肿内的分隔为不完全的，虽然在某些切面上看似乎是多房囊肿，但该囊肿应为单房囊肿。" FontSize="12"/>
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Border>

                        <!-- 报告签署 -->
                        <Border Background="#F0F7FF" CornerRadius="8" Padding="16,12" Margin="0,0,0,20">
                            <TextBlock Text="报告签署" FontWeight="SemiBold" FontSize="16" Foreground="{StaticResource Brush.Primary}"/>
                        </Border>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,16">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="备注：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.Remarks, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Grid.Column="1"/>
                        </Grid>

                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,0">
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <TextBlock Text="录入员：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="0"/>
                            <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.Typist, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Grid.Column="1" Width="120" Margin="0,0,16,0"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="诊断医师：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="2"/>
                            <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.Diagnostician, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Grid.Column="3" Width="120" Margin="0,0,16,0"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="时间：" Style="{StaticResource Text.Label}" Grid.Column="4"/>
                            <TextBox Text="{Binding Report.ReportDate, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}" Grid.Column="5" Width="150"/>
                        </Grid>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Expander>

                <Border Height="60"/>

                </StackPanel>
            </ScrollViewer>

            <!-- Splitter -->
            <GridSplitter Grid.Column="1" 
                         HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" 
                         Background="{StaticResource Brush.Border}" 
                         Width="5"
                         ShowsPreview="True">
                <GridSplitter.Style>
                    <Style TargetType="GridSplitter">
                        <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                        <Style.Triggers>
                            <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsPreviewVisible}" Value="False">
                                <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                            </DataTrigger>
                        </Style.Triggers>
                    </Style>
                </GridSplitter.Style>
            </GridSplitter>

            <!-- Right: Preview Panel -->
            <Border Grid.Column="2" Background="#E9ECEF" BorderBrush="{StaticResource Brush.BorderLight}" BorderThickness="1,0,0,0" Visibility="{Binding IsPreviewVisible, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}">
                <Grid>
                    <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                        <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                    </Grid.RowDefinitions>

                    <!-- Preview Header -->
                    <Border Grid.Row="0" Background="{StaticResource Brush.Primary}" Padding="16,12">
                        <Grid>
                            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            
                            <StackPanel Grid.Column="0" Orientation="Horizontal">
                                <TextBlock Text="📄 实时预览" Foreground="White" FontSize="16" FontWeight="Bold" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                <TextBlock Text="{Binding IsUpdatingPreview, Converter={StaticResource BoolToVis}}" 
                                         Margin="12,0,0,0" 
                                         Foreground="White" 
                                         FontSize="12" 
                                         Opacity="0.9"
                                         VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                    <TextBlock.Style>
                                        <Style TargetType="TextBlock">
                                            <Setter Property="Text" Value="(更新中...)"/>
                                            <Style.Triggers>
                                                <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsUpdatingPreview}" Value="False">
                                                    <Setter Property="Text" Value=""/>
                                                </DataTrigger>
                                            </Style.Triggers>
                                        </Style>
                                    </TextBlock.Style>
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Margin="12,0,0,0" 
                                         Foreground="White" 
                                         FontSize="11" 
                                         Opacity="0.85"
                                         VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                    <TextBlock.Text>
                                        <MultiBinding StringFormat="缩放: {0:F0}%">
                                            <Binding Path="PreviewZoomPercent"/>
                                        </MultiBinding>
                                    </TextBlock.Text>
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>
                            
                            <StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Right">
                                <Button Content="🔍+" 
                                       Command="{Binding ZoomInPreviewCommand}" 
                                       Background="Transparent" 
                                       Foreground="White" 
                                       BorderThickness="0" 
                                       Padding="8,4" 
                                       Cursor="Hand"
                                       ToolTip="放大"
                                       FontSize="14"
                                       Margin="0,0,4,0"/>
                                <Button Content="🔍-" 
                                       Command="{Binding ZoomOutPreviewCommand}" 
                                       Background="Transparent" 
                                       Foreground="White" 
                                       BorderThickness="0" 
                                       Padding="8,4" 
                                       Cursor="Hand"
                                       ToolTip="缩小"
                                       FontSize="14"
                                       Margin="0,0,4,0"/>
                                <Button Content="↻" 
                                       Command="{Binding ResetZoomPreviewCommand}" 
                                       Background="Transparent" 
                                       Foreground="White" 
                                       BorderThickness="0" 
                                       Padding="8,4" 
                                       Cursor="Hand"
                                       ToolTip="重置缩放"
                                       FontSize="14"
                                       Margin="0,0,8,0"/>
                                <Button Content="✕" 
                                       Click="TogglePreview_Click"
                                       Background="Transparent" 
                                       Foreground="White" 
                                       BorderThickness="0" 
                                       Padding="8,4" 
                                       Cursor="Hand"
                                       ToolTip="关闭预览"
                                       FontSize="16"
                                       FontWeight="Bold"/>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Grid>
                    </Border>

                    <!-- Preview Content -->
                    <ScrollViewer x:Name="PreviewScrollViewer" 
                                 Grid.Row="1" 
                                 Style="{StaticResource ModernScrollViewer}"
                                 VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" 
                                 HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" 
                                 Padding="30"
                                 PreviewMouseWheel="PreviewScrollViewer_PreviewMouseWheel"
                                 MouseLeftButtonDown="PreviewScrollViewer_MouseLeftButtonDown"
                                 MouseLeftButtonUp="PreviewScrollViewer_MouseLeftButtonUp"
                                 MouseMove="PreviewScrollViewer_MouseMove">
                        <Grid>
                            <Border Background="White" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Top" Margin="0,10,0,30">
                                <Border.Effect>
                                    <DropShadowEffect Color="#000000" Direction="270" ShadowDepth="4" BlurRadius="20" Opacity="0.2"/>
                                </Border.Effect>
                                <Image x:Name="PreviewImageControl"
                                       Source="{Binding PreviewImage}" 
                                       Stretch="Uniform">
                                    <Image.LayoutTransform>
                                        <ScaleTransform ScaleX="{Binding PreviewZoom}" ScaleY="{Binding PreviewZoom}"/>
                                    </Image.LayoutTransform>
                                </Image>
                            </Border>
                            
                            <!-- No Preview Message -->
                            <TextBlock Text="预览将在您输入数据后自动生成" 
                                     HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                                     VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                     Foreground="{StaticResource Brush.TextSecondary}"
                                     FontSize="14"
                                     TextAlignment="Center">
                                <TextBlock.Style>
                                    <Style TargetType="TextBlock">
                                        <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                                        <Style.Triggers>
                                            <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding PreviewImage}" Value="{x:Null}">
                                                <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                                            </DataTrigger>
                                        </Style.Triggers>
                                    </Style>
                                </TextBlock.Style>
                            </TextBlock>
                        </Grid>
                    </ScrollViewer>
                </Grid>
            </Border>
        </Grid>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <Border Grid.Row="2" Background="White" BorderBrush="{StaticResource Brush.BorderLight}" BorderThickness="0,2,0,0" Padding="32,20">
            <Border.Effect>
                <DropShadowEffect Color="#000000" Direction="270" ShadowDepth="-2" BlurRadius="10" Opacity="0.05"/>
            </Border.Effect>
            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Right">
                <Button Content="🔄 重置表单" Command="{Binding ResetCommand}" Style="{StaticResource Button.Secondary}" Margin="0,0,16,0"/>
                <Button Content="📄 导出 PDF 报告" Style="{StaticResource Button.Primary}" Command="{Binding ExportPdfCommand}">
                    <Button.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect Color="#4A90E2" Direction="270" ShadowDepth="4" BlurRadius="16" Opacity="0.25"/>
                    </Button.Effect>
                </Button>
            </StackPanel>
        </Border>

    </Grid>
</Window>
